name: Jeffery Scott Unwin
part_bio: Peacefully, surrounded by love, after a short but courageous battle with cancer, at his parents' home in Blenheim, on Thursday, July 27, 2023, Jeffrey Scott Unwin of RR 2, Crediton, age 32. Jeff worked for Bluewater Recycling Association in Huron Park for the last 5 years.  He loved baseball and played Slo-Pitch in Seaforth for the Cripplers and Mean Machine.
